data.title: U20W 2024
data.text:
Following the completion of the 1st Round Qualifiers, CEV will confirm the teams qualified to the 2nd Round. Those 2nd Round pools will be defined by the Serpentine System, once the 2nd Round organisers are known and seeded as head of those 2nd Round pools.

1st - Matches Won

2nd - Ranking Points (*Ranking points are awarded for the following results: 3-0 or 3-1: 3 points, 3-2: 2 points, 2-3: 1 point, 1-3 or 0-3: 0 points)

3rd - Match Sets Quotient/Ratio

4th - Match Points Quotient/Ratio

5th - ‘Head to Head’ Results
